subgraph Operations ["Operations"]
    Oinc["++"]
    Oplus["\+"]
    Ominus["−"]
    Omul["×"]
    Odiv["÷"]
    Opow["^"]
    Oeudiv["#/⟡"]
    Omod["⟡"]
    Olog["log(n)"]
    Oroot["^(1/n)"]

    Oinc -->|Iterate| Oplus

    Oplus -->|Invert| Ominus
    Oplus -->|Iterate| Omul

    Omul -->|Decompose| Oeudiv
    Omul -->|Iterate| Opow
    
    Oeudiv -->|Generalize| Odiv
    Oeudiv -->|Remainder| Omod

    Opow -->|Invert| Oroot
    Opow -->|Invert| Olog
end

